<section id="where-to-from-here" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="where-to-from-here">Where to from here?</h2>
<p>Next, we need to tidy up the corpus a bit, and get the text of the articles into R. Then we can get to the meat of the <em>homo calculans</em> project—the <em>discourse</em> of Computational Human Sciences in the 1950s and 60s. What did these early pioneers think they were doing? How did they justify there strange experiments in computational method? I am excited to find out…</p>
